{"tid":2008043,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"CNN:香港有唔少人唔知點解中左肝炎","createTime":"2020-05-08T17:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T08:33:33.000Z","uid":104138,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"68c8f4c7c6f79a94e2b89dfdc14f43efdd27d52f","tid":2008043,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/5550296508/posts/10160826843341509/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F5550296508%2Fposts%2F10160826843341509%2F&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7dxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=29b5168d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/5550296508/posts/10160826843341509/</a><br />\n<br />\n係cnn fb page 勁多鬼佬以為我地食老鼠所以先中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f26c87629cf3b46a62367cfda79ad76230ffc8a","tid":2008043,"uid":62151,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:31:59.000Z","msg":"唔係你以為cnn係美國比人叫極左假新聞係咩原因"},{"pid":"3938fb51d52c63c4a0c9526a68095146f7fc8be5","tid":2008043,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:34:30.000Z","msg":"61歲男子感染大鼠戊型肝炎　暫未確定源頭<br />\n2020-04-30 HKT 20:21<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心正調查一宗人類感染大鼠戊型肝炎個案，患者是一名住在香港仔石排灣邨的61歲男子。<br />\n<br />\n染病男子因長期病患本月7日入住瑪麗醫院接受治療，12日出現肝功能異常，病人情況好轉，昨日轉往東華醫院接受康復治療，病人的血液樣本經檢測後，證實對大鼠戊型肝炎呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心的流行病學調查顯示，病人家居接觸者沒有在住所發現鼠隻或其排泄物，病人於潛伏期內沒有外遊，他的家居接觸者至今沒有出現病徵。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心說，暫未能確定有關感染的源頭及途徑。中心的調查仍在進行中。中心已將個案通報食物環境衞生署的防治蟲鼠事務諮詢組，視乎情況及需要進行防治鼠患工作和調查。"},{"pid":"fb2d84f625e9238681f16f2376a7ef6a69379a56","tid":2008043,"uid":160637,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f26c87629cf3b46a62367cfda79ad76230ffc8a","tid":2008043,"uid":62151,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:31:59.000Z","msg":"唔係你以為cnn係美國比人叫極左假新聞係咩原因"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:51:28.000Z","msg":"唔識就唔好鳩up啦 你可能甚至連條link都未撳落去睇"},{"pid":"af6f9863763af24ceb41b275c0513ef884518e39","tid":2008043,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:51:51.000Z","msg":"本港再度錄得大鼠戊型肝炎個案，衞生防護中心昨公布一名居於香港仔石排灣邨的六十一歲男病人，因長期病患於上月七日入住瑪麗醫院，十二日出現肝功能異常。他其後情況好轉，前日轉往東華醫院接受康復治療，其血液樣本證實對大鼠戊型肝炎呈陽性反應。此宗為今年第二宗感染個案，而本港至今累積感染個案增至十宗。"},{"pid":"303978eebff691f491c5635cf99fee300db24e1b","tid":2008043,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb2d84f625e9238681f16f2376a7ef6a69379a56","tid":2008043,"uid":160637,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f26c87629cf3b46a62367cfda79ad76230ffc8a","tid":2008043,"uid":62151,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:31:59.000Z","msg":"唔係你以為cnn係美國比人叫極左假新聞係咩原因"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:51:28.000Z","msg":"唔識就唔好鳩up啦 你可能甚至連條link都未撳落去睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:57:19.000Z","msg":"呢啲野係相輔相成,報假新聞自然需要有一班會睇假新聞嘅人,好似tvb咁"},{"pid":"b2a4cfe54a439bb9f9d81a065730b065cb037cf3","tid":2008043,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"303978eebff691f491c5635cf99fee300db24e1b","tid":2008043,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb2d84f625e9238681f16f2376a7ef6a69379a56","tid":2008043,"uid":160637,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f26c87629cf3b46a62367cfda79ad76230ffc8a","tid":2008043,"uid":62151,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:31:59.000Z","msg":"唔係你以為cnn係美國比人叫極左假新聞係咩原因"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:51:28.000Z","msg":"唔識就唔好鳩up啦 你可能甚至連條link都未撳落去睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:57:19.000Z","msg":"呢啲野係相輔相成,報假新聞自然需要有一班會睇假新聞嘅人,好似tvb咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:58:29.000Z","msg":"你知唔知篇新聞講咩...."},{"pid":"eb2a954d26ff709b2f3c883874b9b8a92a6f8206","tid":2008043,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T18:01:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cnni/status/1258780988441874433?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcnni%2Fstatus%2F1258780988441874433%3Fs%3D20&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7dxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=ebbc72ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcnni%2Fstatus%2F1258780988441874433%3Fs%3D20&h=1ad290f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cnni/status/1258780988441874433?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\ntwitter都見到有唔少ON9鬼當香港人會食野味<br />\n大家上去正視聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nXiNN <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5485a5ae4559050ae6e09dccf281eb44d0d0d0","tid":2008043,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:06:38.000Z","msg":"要澄清返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c775040ff46b386ce9395ee050338a56b7fa3416","tid":2008043,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"藍店出事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n避免飲用來歷不明的冰塊所調製的飲料。"},{"pid":"03834b1df176b9c7f211df0284fc912db9e0003a","tid":2008043,"uid":345995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:33:33.000Z","msg":"要澄清<br />\nbtw其實歐洲豬都成日奶野啦喺度話我哋食老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年，歐洲食品安全局（EFSA）表示，歐洲人感染戊肝的主因是食用未煮熟的豬肉和豬膶。同年，英國發現從歐洲大陸進口的豬肉香腸帶有戊肝病毒，估計二十萬人受感染。所以，對歐洲進口的豬肉，我們要格外警覺，煮熟才吃。<br />\n--<a href=\"https://livercenter.com.hk/article/關於戊型肝炎和老鼠，你未必知道的七件事/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flivercenter.com.hk%2Farticle%2F%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC%E6%88%8A%E5%9E%8B%E8%82%9D%E7%82%8E%E5%92%8C%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93